data.description: MLS# 270359 Home Sweet Home in Kennewick! This updated rambler offers both affordability and tons of charm. Whether you're a first-time home buyer or an investor looking for a rental opportunity, this property ticks all the boxes. Step into this updated home and experience the warmth and comfort it has to offer. With hardwood flooring and large windows in the living room, natural light fills the space, creating a welcoming interior. The kitchen features updated wood cabinetry, a pantry for all your storage needs, and tile backsplash & floors. Adjacent to the kitchen is a convenient dining area that overlooks the deck and backyard, providing the perfect setting for enjoying meals. This home offers a comfortable living space of 1464 sq ft, providing plenty of room for everyone, with 3 bedrooms, a bonus room, and 2 renovated  bathrooms. The primary bedroom is a tranquil retreat with its abundance of windows that flood the room with natural light. It also has private access to the deck, creating a perfect spot for your morning coffee. The beautifully updated private bathroom features a barn-style door, adding a touch of rustic charm. In addition to its interior features, this home boasts a gorgeous backyard, perfect for outdoor gatherings and enjoying the pleasant weather. You will find full fencing in the front and back, a nice deck & patio for lounging or entertaining, gorgeous mature landscaping with flowering bushes and a fruit tree. The home also has a storage building in the back yard, providing options for storing your outdoor equipment and gardening supplies. This home comes complete with a comprehensive home inspection and a 1 year home warranty! Conveniently located near Park Middle School and Kennewick High School, with nearby shopping and downtown amenities. Don't miss the chance to make this updated and adorable home your own. Schedule a viewing today!
